    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "发现本题明显可以写出<strong>转移方程</strong>，设 $dp[i]$：第 $i$ 位受影响后的最大高度。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "对于前 $i$ 个，可以得到 $dp[i] = min(a[i], dp[i - 1] + 1)$；",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "对于后 $i$ 个，可以得到 $dp[i] = min(a[i], dp[i + 1] + 1)$。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "这个 $dp$ 拆成两个，整成<strong>前后缀 dp</strong>，这题也就结束了。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "void solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tint n; cin >> n;\n\tvar a = vector<int>(n + 1);\n\tfa(i, 1, n)cin >> a[i];\n\tvar pre = vector<int>(n + 1);\n\tvar suf = vector<int>(n + 1);\n\tpre[1] = a[1], suf[n] = a[n];\n\tfa(i, 2, n)pre[i] = min(a[i], pre[i - 1] + 1);\n\tfb(i, n - 1, 1)suf[i] = min(a[i], suf[i + 1] + 1);\n\tll ans = 0;\n\tfa(i, 1, n)ans += a[i] - min(pre[i], suf[i]);\n\tcout << ans << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
